    IsCompact (X := X) U ‚Üî ‚àÉ s : Set X.affineOpens, s.Finite ‚àß U = ‚®Ü i ‚àà s, (i : X.Opens) := by
  convert isCompact_and_isOpen_iff_finite_and_eq_biUnion_affineOpens (U := U.1) using 4 with s
  ¬∑ simp [U.isOpen]
